@page "/returns"
@layout Layout.StoreLayout

<PageTitle>Returns Policy - Victoria James Store</PageTitle>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 md:py-20 animate-fade-in">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-8">Returns & Refunds Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none text-on-surface-variant space-y-6">
        <p>At Victoria James Store, we take pride in the quality of our products. We inspect all items before dispatch to ensure they are in perfect condition. However, if you receive a damaged or incorrect item, we are here to help.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-8 mb-4">1. Conditions for Returns</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>The item must be unused, in the same condition that you received it, and in its original packaging.</li>
            <li>Returns are only accepted for items that are factory defective or damaged upon delivery.</li>
            <li>You must report the issue to us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of receiving your delivery.</li>
            <li>Change of mind is not an acceptable reason for a return.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-8 mb-4">2. How to Request a Return</h2>
        <p>To initiate a return, please contact our support team immediately via WhatsApp at <strong>0816 280 9886</strong> or email us at <strong>support@victoriajames.com</strong>. You will need to provide:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Your Order Number.</li>
            <li>A clear video or photograph showing the defect or damage.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-8 mb-4">3. Refunds & Replacements</h2>
        <p>Once your return is received and inspected, we will notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund/replacement.</p>
        <p>If approved, we will either send a replacement item at no extra shipping cost to you, or process a full refund to your original bank account within 3-5 working days.</p>

        <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/30 mt-8">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Need immediate assistance?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">Reach out to our dedicated support line on WhatsApp. We typically respond within minutes during business hours.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>